      | Identifier | Name                                 | OPT.IsVendor | OPT.IsCustomer | M_PricingSystem_ID.Identifier |
      | bpartner_1 | BPartnerTest_ManuallyPickedLockedHUs | N            | Y              | pricingSys_1                  |
